edu.snu.onyx.runtime.executor.data.metadata

Class LocalFileMetadata<K extends Serializable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.snu.onyx.runtime.executor.data.metadata.FileMetadata<K>
      • edu.snu.onyx.runtime.executor.data.metadata.LocalFileMetadata<K>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the key type of its partitions.

    @ThreadSafe
public final class LocalFileMetadata<K extends Serializable>
extends FileMetadata<K>
    This class represents a metadata for a local file Block. It resides in local only, and does not synchronize with master.
